dataList.content: Okay~ The end of the game is nigh!
The stage shrinks once again! Looks like today's cardio day for everyone, huh?
It shrinks and shrinks... and now it has corralled the contestants a floor below, to the basements!
Things are really going to get interesting from here on out, so don't take your eyes off the spectacle!
This... this place looks even more deserted than the upstairs.
This looks like just another lab, but...
I wonder what they did down here?
A notable difference is that there is nothing left in here.
That is a correct observation. This is where it must have begun.
Everything that was connected to the taboo.
The number of remaining candidates is still shrinking.
We need only collect the coins. Do not lose sight of our mission, no matter what.
Outis gave us a consistent and constant stream of encouragements as we moved from room to room.
